{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"539370-di-mana-sekolahmu","title":"Di Mana Sekolahmu?","description":"Sekolah bukan hanya untuk anak-anak! Dalam perjalanannya ke sekolah, Pintoo menemukan beberapa sekolah yang menarik! Apakah kamu ingin melihat sekolah-sekolah itu? Lihatlah ke dalam!","language":"Bahasa Indonesia","langCode":"id","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Amalia Nindy Astuti"],"illustrators":["Sushant Ahire"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Badan Pengembangan dan Pembinaan Bahasa","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/539370-di-mana-sekolahmu"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727493/size3/21776053ccf55e215d97c6b50d6c8bc5.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727493/size6/21776053ccf55e215d97c6b50d6c8bc5.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/468875/size6/fcd43f8c8c65b4fbfb05dbd1214499e6.jpg","text":"Aku pergi ke sekolah setiap hari.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/468877/size6/53e9e16dc477d014cc97f1d17cd67be6.jpg","text":"Aku dan Chiki melihat\nbanyak sekolah dalam perjalanan kami.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460766/size6/6c551cf23a35dab4d00e61ea247fd8c2.jpg","text":"Burung-burung beo terbang menuju sekolah di atas pohon jambu.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460768/size6/39bf0e7aa77ad859d5a12a6dc89ac4bc.jpg","text":"Tupai-tupai lari menuju sekolah di atas pohon mangga.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illus